  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.2.2",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.2.2",
  "body": "## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from the [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Download:\r\n  - Reduced the notification priority of the JVM runtime service\r\n  - Added progress and description to notifications during Forge-like installer installation\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- LWJGL:\r\n  - Fixed Vulkan Mod failing to run due to missing UNSAFE\r\n  - Fixed Minecraft 1.7.2 failing to launch properly\r\n  - Fixed critical LWJGL-OpenGL mapping errors\r\n  - Fixed certain versions of JourneyMap preventing the game from launching (rendering issues may still persist)"
